Damn it!

840
01:30:17,840 --> 01:30:20,593
How pathetic.

841
01:30:20,680 --> 01:30:23,319
Killed by the same man
that killed his father.

842
01:30:24,840 --> 01:30:26,831
You killed my father?

843
01:30:26,960 --> 01:30:29,076
Oh, yes.

844
01:30:29,160 --> 01:30:30,513
As I will you.

845
01:30:48,520 --> 01:30:49,873
Well, well.

846
01:30:51,040 --> 01:30:54,828
One thing is certain:
You are no Musketeer.

847
01:31:03,000 --> 01:31:05,833
I might have been mistaken.

848
01:31:23,200 --> 01:31:24,758
For you, Father.

849
01:32:30,400 --> 01:32:34,029
- Where have you been?
- Taking care of something ugly.

850
01:32:40,000 --> 01:32:41,592
Richelieu!

851
01:32:41,720 --> 01:32:43,950
You're too late, Musketeers!

852
01:32:44,080 --> 01:32:47,152
By now the Duke of Buckingham's
signature is next to mine.

853
01:32:47,240 --> 01:32:49,276
The alliance is complete!

854
