That would be difficult, considering
the treaty never left France!

855
01:32:53,760 --> 01:32:55,751
A minor problem.

856
01:32:55,840 --> 01:32:58,274
I will return twice as strong...

857
01:32:58,400 --> 01:33:01,198
and the throne will be mine!

858
01:33:03,520 --> 01:33:04,635
I think not.

859
01:33:10,320 --> 01:33:12,754
You will never harm...

860
01:33:12,840 --> 01:33:14,671
another soul ever again.

861
01:33:14,760 --> 01:33:16,591
My promise to God.

862
01:33:16,680 --> 01:33:18,159
Wait!

863
01:33:26,080 --> 01:33:27,877
Well done, Your Majesty.

864
01:33:34,040 --> 01:33:35,837
Are you all right?

865
01:33:37,240 --> 01:33:38,559
Yes.

866
01:33:57,640 --> 01:33:58,993
Arise.

867
01:34:01,200 --> 01:34:04,033
Is this the man
who saved my life?

868
01:34:04,160 --> 01:34:06,958
His name's D'Artagnan, Sire.

869
01:34:07,040 --> 01:34:11,750
D'Artagnan, I am in your debt. What can
I do to repay the courage you've shown me?

870
01:34:14,640 --> 01:34:17,757
Your Majesty, his heart
has but one desire...

871
01:34:17,880 --> 01:34:20,474
and that is to become
a Musketeer.

872
01:34:20,600 --> 01:34:22,318
Then approach.

873
01:34:26,080 --> 01:34:27,433
Kneel.

874
01:34:35,040 --> 01:34:38,510
This world is an uncertain
realm, filled with danger...

875
01:34:38,600 --> 01:34:41,273
honour undermined
by the pursuit of power...

876
01:34:41,400 --> 01:34:44,472
freedom sacrificed when the weak
are oppressed by the strong.

877
01:34:45,920 --> 01:34:49,469
But there are those who
oppose these powerful forces...

878
01:34:49,600 --> 01:34:53,479
