to truth, honour and freedom.

879
01:34:54,720 --> 01:34:56,915
These men are known
as Musketeers.

880
01:35:02,520 --> 01:35:04,317
Rise, D'Artagnan...

881
01:35:05,680 --> 01:35:07,159
and join them.

882
01:35:13,240 --> 01:35:15,595
Long live the Musketeers!

883
01:35:46,720 --> 01:35:50,110
Your father would be proud
of you; you are a Musketeer.

884
01:35:50,240 --> 01:35:53,118
